Ext.data.JsonP['Widget_Configuration_File_(widget.json)']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Widget Configuration File (widget.json)</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-35620081\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Widget Configuration File (widget.json)</h1>\n    <p>All widgets have a configuration file called <tt class=\" \">widget.json</tt> located in the root directory of the widget. The configuration file follows the <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://npmjs.org/doc/json.html\" target=\"_blank\">npm package.json format</a> with a few exceptions.    </p>\n    <p>The widget configuration file also accepts the following key-value pairs:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Key    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Value    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Description    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>id    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>String    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">Mandatory.</strong> Needs to be the same name as the widget root folder.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>copyright    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>String    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Widget copyright information.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>license    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>String    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Widget license information.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>min-alloy-version*    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Float    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Minimum required Alloy version to run the widget.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>min-titanium-version*    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Float    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Minimum required Titanium version to run the widget.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>tags    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>String    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>List of keywords.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>platforms*    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Any combination of platforms (comma delimited)    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Which platforms the widget will run on.    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    <p>(*) Currently, the min-alloy-version, min-titanium-version and platforms keys are not required, but in the future, Alloy will perform a check against these values.    </p>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=35620081\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Widget Configuration File (widget.json)"});